Key of the Sun
NPC drop system was fully reworked and expanded
Arch Imp, Firebird, Heater, Winged Heater, Lava Jellyfish, Spore Slinger and Spore Smasher now drop Vortex (1% chance)
Cacodemon now drops Vortex (5% chance) and Bloody Whetstone (≈3% chance)
Ifrit now drops Vortex (10% chance)
Charging Spearbones, Centurions, Geomancer, Shaft Sentinel, Skeleton Trapper, Dragon Skull, Vampire Miner and Archdruid now drop Soulless Locket (1% chance)
Hunter now drops Hidden Blade (10% chance)
Flesh Mummy and Shadow Mummy now drop Hidden Blade (1% chance)
Flesh Slime and Flesh Axe now drop Golden Shield (1% chance)
Zombie Tactical, Coldmando, Mister Shotty and Snowman Trasher now drop Ammo Magazine (1% chance)
Orb of Corruption, Shadow Slime and Shadow Hammer now drop Greek Extinguisher (1% chance)
Radiators now drop Six Hundred Watt Lightbulb (1% chance)
Spectral Gastropod and Spectral Mummy now drop Arcane Shard (12.5% chance) and Rubber Boot (1% chance)
Dragon Hornet now drops Strong Venom (≈14% chance)
Skeleton Bat now drops Rubybead Herb and Mystical Claw (≈14% each) and Breeze Shard (10% chance, 1–2)
Fleder, Gargoyle, Demonic Spirit and Valkyrie now drop Mystical Claw (≈14% chance)
Infected Man, Frozen Nimbus, Frozen Soul and Giant Albino Charger now drop Element Dust (≈14% chance)
Flesh Slime, Shadow Slime, Sludger and Tiny Toxic Sludge now drop Dew of Herbs (≈14% chance)
Vile Decomposer and Dragon Snatcher now drop Dew Orb (≈14% chance)
Wyverns now drop Mystical Totem (≈14% chance) and Breeze Shards
Backwoods Raven, Fleder, Gargoyle, Valkyrie, Frozen Nimbus and Wyverns now drop Breeze Shards (10% chance, 1–2)
Wyverns additionally drop Wyvern Fur
Corrupt enemies (slimes, mummies, axes, corruption constructs) now drop Corrupt Shards (25% chance, 1–2)
Fire-type enemies (Cacodemon, Arch Demon, Arch Imp, Heater, Ifrit) now drop Fire Shards (50% chance, 2–4)
Frost enemies (Draug variants, Frozen enemies, Cold Father) now drop Frost Shards (10% chance, 1–2)
Toxic enemies (Infected Man, Dragon Snatcher, Dragon Hornet) now drop Toxin Shards (10% chance, 1–2)
Queen Bee now drops Toxin Shards (25% chance, 2–6)
Undead enemies (Radiant Bones, Skeletons, Dungeon mobs) now drop Undead Shards (10% chance, 1–2)
Water creatures (Orca) now drop Water Shards (25% chance, 1–2)
Temple Golem now drops Sun’s Shadow (10% chance)
Ent now drops Verdant Staff (10% chance)
Hog now drops Suspicious Bag (≈11% chance)
Archdruid now drops Broken Dice (≈11% chance)
Spectral Elemental and Albino Antlion now drop Suspicious Bag
Sap Slime now drops Sap (20% chance)
Cold Father now drops Soul of Ice (guaranteed, 3–6)
Irate Bones now drop Ancient Scrap (≈14% chance)
Blaze now drops Blazes (25% chance)
All tactical and special zombies now drop Rotten Flesh (10% chance, 1–2) these enemies also have a chance to drop Soulless Locket
Mothron now drops Broken Glaive and Broken Spear (25% chance each)
Valid enemies now drop Rough Leather or Animal Leather (12.5% chance) like in RoA
Deer Skull, Bone Fish and Dragon Skull now drop Necro Buckler (10% chance)
Spectral Elemental now drops Chaos Flicker (4% chance)
Lihzahrd Trickster now drops Chaos Flicker (2% chance)
Spectral Elemental now additionally drops Arcane Shard
